RawLine: ITEM_202121_Tip,棺馬寨內關卡通關專用的令牌，但不能用於自由進出各房舍，只有少數棺馬賊持有。,棺马寨内关卡通关专用的令牌，但不能用于自由进出各房舍，只有少数棺马贼持有。

Items.mt: The token is used to pass through the cartoon gate in the coffin horse fortress, but it cannot be used to enter or leave the rooms freely, only a few coffin horse thieves have it.
